{"tid":1615741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明報話開實彈射手足係警署警長曾家輝喎","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T12:48:51.000Z","uid":68738,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac9950385f4fd5ff368193cba0763987557243e1","tid":1615741,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:45:03.000Z","msg":"另曾志健和邱宏達則被控於同日在荃灣大河道、大河道北和鱟地坊一帶，與其他不知名者參與暴動。曾志健另被控兩項襲警罪，指他於同日在荃灣鱟地坊一帶，襲擊警員謝思明和警署警長曾家輝。當中曾家輝為當日開槍射向曾志健左胸的警長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191003/s00001/1570086665549/【十一-示威】中槍男生控暴動襲警留醫未能出庭-身旁被制服理大生同遭起訴\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191003%2Fs00001%2F1570086665549%2F%E3%80%90%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E6%A7%8D%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%95%99%E9%86%AB%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%87%BA%E5%BA%AD-%E8%BA%AB%E6%97%81%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8C%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=5529f198\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191003%2Fs00001%2F1570086665549%2F%E3%80%90%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E6%A7%8D%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%95%99%E9%86%AB%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E5%87%BA%E5%BA%AD-%E8%BA%AB%E6%97%81%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E5%90%8C%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4&h=8f45a4e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191003/s00001/1570086665549/【十一-示威】中槍男生控暴動襲警留醫未能出庭-身旁被制服理大生同遭起訴</a>"},{"pid":"35a13abd9159c3e2187f2049f1ccdee590786e2d","tid":1615741,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"高端化妝之學術討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615130</a><br